          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The target was a solid natural graphite slice thick",
                "enough (1 mm) to stop the 12-C beam particles.  Because",
                "of the 1.1% content of 13-C in used target, the",
                "formation of excited 24-Mg through the reaction",
                " 13-C(12-C,n)24-MG, that would contaminate the",
                "measurements, has to be evaluated by authors.  13-C",
                "influence is negligible."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "-By authors:",
                "1.  It is clear that direct detection of gamma rays",
                "from the first excited states will not yield the total",
                "cross sections. Besides direct feeding of the ground",
                "states in 20-Ne, 23-Na and 23-Mg from the compound",
                "nucleus 24-Mg, there are cases where the residual",
                "nuclei decay by gamma emission from excited states",
                "other than the first one, directly to the ground state.",
                "2.  Cross section gamma-rays production obtained",
                "through a polynomial fit of the yield."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "FACILITY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "VDGT"
                ],
                "institute": "3MEXUMX"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The 3 MV Pelletron."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "EXTB",
                "SITA"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " To reduce the counting time in the",
                "experiment, and minimize the contribution from",
                "background radiation, beams as intense as 10-15",
                "electric muA were used.  Depending on the beam energy",
                "and charge-state distribution, the 2+, 3+ and 4+ states",
                "were used."
              ]
            }
          ],
